*xscreensaver-5.03-r5 (28 Mar 2008)

  28 Mar 2008; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +xscreensaver-5.03-r5.ebuild, -xscreensaver-5.03-r4.ebuild,
  Add IUSE core-deps to remove dependency on jpeg.

*xscreensaver-5.03-r4 (14 Feb 2008)

  14 Feb 2008; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +xscreensaver-5.03-r4.ebuild, -xscreensaver-5.03-r3.ebuild,
  +files/xscreensaver-5.03-clip-allow-adm-lock.patch:
  Remove hardcoded checks for 'adm' username (or 'sys', or 'operator')
  that disable locking. These are not priviledged accounts on CLIP, and
  'adm' is typically used for an ADMIN account.

*xscreensaver-5.03-r3 (16 Jan 2008)

  16 Jan 2008; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +xscreensaver-5.03-r3.ebuild, -xscreensaver-5.03-r2.ebuild:
  Remove dependency on glib through IUSE clip-deps.

