*xscreensaver-5.03-r1 (26 Oct 2007)

  26 Oct 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +xscreensaver-5.03-r1.ebuild, files/XscreenSaver:
  App-defaults file adapted to lock the session after 5 minutes of
  inactivity by default.

*xscreensaver-5.03 (12 Oct 2007)

  12 Oct 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  xscreensaver-5.03.ebuild, +files/XscreenSaver, 
  +files/xscreensaver-5.03-clip-fr.patch:
  Initial CLIP import. CPREFIX fixes. Add IUSE clip that:
    - removes all animated screensavers
    - removes the 'demo' GUI
    - removes the associated dependencies
    - turns the 'lock' GUI hardcoded strings to French
    - installs a custom app-defaults file with more localized
      stuff
    - removes some unsupported X11 extensions from the configuration,
      and compiles in support for external password checkers so that
      we can use app-clip/xscreensaver-pwcheck.
